{
  "texts": [
    "FLAG_SP_SNReach sky tile.",
    "Use SKYTILE+ID_SRC to identify the corresponding source products UID Integer unique detection ID.",
    "It equals CatID×10 11 +SKYTILE×10 5 +ID_SRC, where CatID is 1 for the 1B detected Main and Supp catalogs and 2 for the 3B detected Hard catalog.",
    "UID_Hard Hard catalog UID of the source with a strong association, or -UID if the association is weak.",
    "0 means no counterpart found in the Hard catalog."
  ]
}